OL,3,CCarrie Johnson describes 'relief' as
OL,4,Crapist John Worboys denied release
OL,6,FCarrie Johnson has described her
OL,7,F"relief" as black cab rapist John
OL,8,FWorboys was refused parole for a
OL,9,Fsecond time.
OL,11,FThe taxi driver, who has been in jail
OL,12,Fsince 2009 for drugging and sexually
OL,13,Fassaulting multiple female passengers,
OL,14,Fwas refused release as well as
OL,15,Ftransfer to an open prison, a
OL,16,Fspokesperson for the Parole Board said.
OL,18,FThe panel were not satisfied that
OL,19,FWorboys no longer posed a risk to the
OL,20,Fpublic, the spokesperson said in a
OL,21,Fstatement published on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
