OL,3,CCarrie Johnson describes 'relief' as
OL,4,Crapist John Worboys denied release
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FJohnson, the wife of former Prime
OL,12,FMinister Boris Johnson, was drugged by
OL,13,FWorboys and previously gave evidence
OL,14,Fagainst him, which ensured he was kept
OL,15,Fin prison.
OL,17,F"It has been a hugely anxious wait
OL,18,Fknowing that Worboys was up for parole
OL,19,Fagain," Johnson wrote on X on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
