OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778825170
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson describes 'relief' as
OL,4,Crapist John Worboys denied release
OL,6,F"The relief I feel knowing that he
OL,7,Fwill remain behind bars is hard to put
OL,8,Finto words. Women and girls across
OL,9,FBritain are safer as a result of this
OL,10,Fdecision."
OL,12,FWorboys was first jailed in 2009 for
OL,13,F19 sexual offences linked to attacks
OL,14,Fon 12 victims between October 2006 and
OL,15,FFebruary 2008 in London, and given an
OL,16,Findefinite sentence for public
OL,17,Fprotection with a minimum term of
OL,18,Feight years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
