PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778825170
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson describes 'relief' as
OL,4,Crapist John Worboys denied release
OL,6,FThe offences included one count of
OL,7,Frape, five sexual assaults, one
OL,8,Fattempted assault and 12 drugging
OL,9,Fcharges.
OL,11,FIn December 2017, a parole board panel
OL,12,Fdecided he was ready for release,
OL,13,Fsparking a legal challenge by two of
OL,14,Fhis victims that overturned the
OL,15,Fdecision.
OL,17,FAmid outrage over the battle, rules
OL,18,Fwere then changed to allow some parole
OL,19,Fhearings to be held in public and
OL,20,Fpermit better scrutiny of the
OL,21,Fprocesses used.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
