PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778825170
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson describes 'relief' as
OL,4,Crapist John Worboys denied release
OL,6,FThe publicity around the case led
OL,7,Ffurther victims to come forward, and
OL,8,FWorboys was charged with more offences
OL,9,Fdating between 2000 and 2008, which he
OL,10,Fadmitted.
OL,12,FIn 2019 he was given two life
OL,13,Fsentences with a minimum term of six
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,F'Believe Me', a four-part miniseries
OL,17,Fdetailing Worboys' victims' fight for
OL,18,Fjustice, started on ITV on May 10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
