OL,3,CCarrie Johnson describes 'relief' as
OL,4,Crapist John Worboys denied release
OL,6,FUnder current legislation Worboys will
OL,7,Fbe eligible for a further review in
OL,8,Fdue course, the Parole Board
OL,9,Fspokesperson said.
OL,11,FThe date of the next review will be
OL,12,Fset by the Ministry of Justice, they
OL,13,Fsaid.
